# Project Atlas — Atlas Finance API v2.3 (build close-out)

@D atlas-finance-api|Atlas finance API at end of build|2.3.0|https://api.acme.internal/finance/v2

@AUTH bearer|JWT bearer issued by Acme SSO|Authorization
@AUTH service_token|mTLS service-to-service token|x-service-token

@S CutoverStatus|Live cutover status reporting
 phase|string|required||SHADOW_WRITE|READ_CUTOVER|FULL_CUTOVER
 startedAt|string|required|date-time|Phase start
 reconciliationMatch|number|required||Pct match between legacy and Atlas
 healthy|boolean|required||Whether all dimensions are within tolerance

@S WaiveRequest|Request body for the recon gate waive endpoint
 reason|string|required||Free-text justification (audited)
 approver|string|required||Approver identity
 evidenceUrl|string|||Optional link to supporting evidence

@EP GET /cutover/status|Current cutover phase and health|getCutoverStatus
@EP POST /cutover/advance|Advances cutover to the next phase (requires approval)|advanceCutover
@EP POST /cutover/rollback|Rolls cutover back one phase|rollbackCutover
@EP GET /audit/stream|Server-sent stream of audit events|streamAudit

@R WaiveRequest -> CutoverStatus|references|Waive requests are scoped to a cutover phase
